      excerpt:
        "Greetings from Procopio Towle Dental Office! As many of you are still working remotely from home, getting ready for cooler weather, making upcoming holiday plans and more, you may not be thinking about your available or unused dental insurance benefits. Whether you have insurance benefits remaining or if you have funds set aside in a [&hellip;]",
      author: "Dr. Tiziana Procopio",
      content:
        '<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\nGreetings from Procopio Towle Dental Office!\n\nAs many of you are still working remotely from home, getting ready for cooler weather, making upcoming holiday plans and more, you may not be thinking about your available or unused dental insurance benefits. Whether you have insurance benefits remaining or if you have funds set aside in a flexible spending account (FSA) or healthcare saving account (HSA), now might be a good time to schedule treatment so your patient portion amount can be applied to this year\u2019s deductions. Please check that you have used all available benefits to complete any outstanding treatment or for all-important preventive dental hygiene appointment (\u201ccheckup and cleaning\u201d). Most plans do not allow rollover unused dollars to the next benefit year and have a\u00a0<em><strong>\u201cUse \u2018Em or Lose \u2018Em!\u201d</strong></em>\u00a0approach - now is the time to get it done!\n\nWe still have a few available appointments!! Please <a href="tel:925-933-5677">contact</a> our office today to schedule your appointment as we find that the upcoming holiday season is one of our busiest periods.\n\nOur selected Saturdays for the rest of this year are\u00a0<em><strong>November 13, 2021 and December 11, 2021.</strong></em>\n\nIf you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact our office.\n\nBest Regards,\nDr. Procopio',
