      author: "Dr. Tiziana Procopio",
      content:
        'To Our Dear Patients:\n\nWe trust this message finds you and your families in good health and spirit.\n\nAs we go through the extension of \u201cShelter-in-Place\u201d to May 31, 2020, we wanted to stay connected and assure you that we will continue to be open for dental emergency appointments on:\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Monday, Wednesday, and\u00a0Friday\u00a0\u00a0 11:00 AM \u2013 3:00 PM</strong></p>\nAs a friendly reminder, if you are unable to reach a live team member during our modified office hours above, please leave a voicemail and/or email and your message will be returned within 24 hours.\u00a0If you contact our office after hours, please call<strong>\u00a0<a href="tel:(925) 933-5677">(925) 933-5677</a>\u00a0and press 2\u00a0</strong>and your call will be forwarded directly to Dr. Procopio or by email at <a href="mailto:office@procopiodds.com"><strong>office@procopiodds.com</strong></a>\n\nWe are in the process of rescheduling all appointments for the month of <strong>May</strong> <strong>2020</strong>. If your insurance coverage is approaching termination, please reach out to our office by email. Again, we want to personally\u00a0THANK\u00a0each one of you for your understanding and patience during these challenging times.\n\nBest Regards to all and please stay safe,\nTiziana Procopio Towle, DDS',
