      author: "Dr. Tiziana Procopio",
      content:
        'To Our Dear Patients:\n\nWith the current extension of the \u201cShelter-in-Place\u201d Order and concerns surrounding the coronavirus (COVID-19), we expect our office to be closed\u00a0until<strong> Sunday, May 3, 2020</strong>. For the remainder of this week ending April 3, 2020, we will continue to be open for emergency appointments only on:\n<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><strong>Wednesday 4/1/2020\u00a0\u00a0 2:00 PM \u2013 5:00 PM</strong>\n<strong>Friday 4/3/2020\u00a0\u00a0 11:00 AM \u2013 2:00 PM</strong></p>\n<strong>Starting\u00a0Monday, April 6, 2020</strong>\u00a0we will be open for emergency appointments only on:\n<p style="padding-left: 40px;"><strong>Monday, Wednesday, and\u00a0Friday\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 11:00 AM \u2013 3:00PM</strong></p>\nAs a friendly reminder, if you are unable to reach a live team member during our \u201copen for emergencies only\u201d days and hours above, please leave a voicemail and/or email and your message will be returned within 24 hours.\u00a0 If you contact our office after hours, please call<strong>\u00a0<a href="tel:(925) 933-5677">(925) 933-5677</a>\u00a0and press 2</strong>,\u00a0and your call will be forwarded directly to Dr. Procopio.\n\nProcopio Towle Dental Office team is proactive in screening patients before initiating dental procedures including the following: disclosure of any recent traveling in last month and presentation of any flu-like symptoms. We will have limited team members and one patient at a time to allow for social distancing, as well as complete disinfection of the office between procedures.\u00a0Our clinical team diligently wears personal-protective equipment (PPE) and have taken an extra step by wearing disposable attire \u2013 gowns, masks (N95), gloves, and shoe booties. We also provide shoe covers (or \u201cbooties\u201d) for patient use when entering our office.\n\nWe are in the process of rescheduling all appointments for the month of April 2020. We want to personally\u00a0<strong>THANK\u00a0</strong>each one of you for your understanding and patience during these challenging times.\n\nWe can always be reached at<strong>\u00a0<a href="tel:(925) 933-5677">(925) 933-5677</a>\u00a0</strong>or by email at\u00a0<a href="mailto:office@procopiodds.com"><strong>office@procopiodds.com</strong></a>\n\nBest Regards,\nTiziana Procopio Towle, DDS',
