      title: "An UPDATE from Procopio Towle Dental Office about COVID-19",
      excerpt:
        "To Our Dear Patients: With all the developments and concerns surrounding the coronavirus (COVID-19), and in particular its potential impact on our office and the well-being of our patients, \u201cThe California Dental Association (CDA) has strongly recommended that dentists practicing in California voluntarily suspend nonessential or non-urgent dental care for the next 14 days.\u201d With [&hellip;]",
      author: "Dr. Tiziana Procopio",
      content:
        'To Our Dear Patients:\n\nWith all the developments and concerns surrounding the coronavirus (COVID-19), and in particular its potential impact on our office and the well-being of our patients, <em><strong>\u201cThe California Dental Association (CDA) has strongly recommended that dentists practicing in California voluntarily suspend nonessential or non-urgent dental care for the next 14 days.\u201d </strong></em>With that being said and to better serve you during the next 14 days our office will be open for emergency appointments only on:\n\n<strong>Monday - 3/23/2020 and 3/30/2020\u00a0\u00a0 2:00 PM \u2013 5:00 PM</strong>\n<strong>Wednesday \u2013 3/18/2020, 3/25/2020 and 4/1/2020\u00a0\u00a0 2:00 PM \u2013 5:00 PM</strong>\n<strong>Friday \u2013 3/20/2020, 3/24/2020 and 4/3/2020\u00a0\u00a0 11:00 AM \u2013 2:00 PM</strong>\n\nIf you are unable to reach a live staff member during our said days and hours above, please leave a voicemail and/or email and your message will be returned within 24 hours.\n\nIf you contact our office after hours, please call <strong><a href="tel:9259335677">(925) 933-5677</a> and press 2</strong>, your call will be forwarded directly to Dr. Procopio.\n\nWe expect our office to be closed until <strong>Friday, April 3, 2020</strong>. We have done our best to reschedule all the appointments in order to limit and preserve health of our patients. As part of the Procopio Towle Dental Office, we want to wish you and your loved ones well. Our thoughts go out to all those who have been affected by this virus and all the caregivers working tirelessly on the front lines of this crisis. We strive to provide only the highest quality of dental care to our patients. Thank you so much for your understanding in these tough times, but know that we at Procopio Towle Dental office are here to help in any way.\n\nWe can always be reached at <a href="tel:(925) 933-5677"><strong>(925) 933-5677</strong></a> or by email at <a href="mailto:office@procopiodds.com"><strong>office@procopiodds.com</strong></a>\n\nBest Regards,\nTiziana Procopio Towle, DDS',
