  //     "Many people suffer from dental problems like overbite, underbite, or crowded teeth. It severely impacts how they interact with people and become unhappy with their smiles. As a result, this reduces their self-esteem, making it difficult to meet people. Thanks to modern dentistry offer numerous ways to cure these problems. Braces and Invisalign both have [&hellip;]",
  //   author: "Procopio Towle Dental Office",
  //   content:
  //     '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many people suffer from dental problems like overbite, underbite, or crowded teeth. It severely impacts how they interact with people and become unhappy with their smiles. As a result, this reduces their self-esteem, making it difficult to meet people. Thanks to modern dentistry offer numerous ways to cure these problems. Braces and Invisalign both have their advantages. However, this article will focus on the benefits of Invisalign over regular braces.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"align":"right","id":5668,"width":274,"height":195,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image alignright size-full is-resized"><img src="https://pwdds.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/662.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-5668" width="274" height="195"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":4} -->\n<h4>What are Braces?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Braces are teeth-straightening dental tools using plastic or metal brackets, wires, or rubber bands. It corrects dental issues like crooked teeth, crowding, or teeth alignment. However, many people still use them to fix their dental problems. Living with braces requires altering daily life skills.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":4} -->\n<h4>What is Invisalign?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Invisible aligners or Invisalign offers a revolutionary dental treatment to correct teeth problems. They are nearly invisible and perfect for people who cannot wear braces; they are self-conscious about being noticed in public. Invisalign are custom-made, clear braces that help straighten teeth without using metal braces. They are transparent devices that adjust teeth to their appropriate place and help achieve a beautiful smile.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":4} -->\n<h4>Benefits of Invisalign Over Regular Braces?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Invisalign has plenty of benefits over regular braces. They are easy to clean, require fewer dental visits, offer great convenience, and much more. Let\u2019s get to know the benefits in a bit more detail.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":5} -->\n<h5>No food restrictions</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Aligners are removable, and you can eat and drink whatever you want. There are no food restrictions with Invisalign because one can remove them when they are having their meal. In contrast, some food restrictions with regular braces might frustrate people\u2014for instance, sticky or hard foods like crunchy vegetables, nuts, candies, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":5} -->\n<h5>Easy to clean</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Invisalign is super easy to clean than traditional braces. It isn\'t easy to clean your brackets appropriately, especially when traveling on vacation. At the same time, Invisalign offers excellent ease of comfort to the users. You must remove the aligner trays and gently brush them with warm water and toothpaste. That\u2019s it, and you are ready to reinstall them in your mouth after adequate cleaning.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":5} -->\n<h5>Fewer dental visits</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Invisalign is best for busy people who cannot maintain regular braces. It requires fewer dental visits and gives you the freedom to carry on your daily activities with ease. Metal braces require various dental visits to tighten the wires or rubber bands to ensure teeth repositioning and alignment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"align":"right","id":5669,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image alignright size-full"><img src="https://pwdds.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/663.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-5669"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":5} -->\n<h5>Look better</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Invisalign looks better than regular braces and helps to hide ongoing dental treatment. Many people are self-conscious and don\u2019t want to discuss the dental treatment they are going through. Invisalign is nearly invisible, and anyone can hardly get to know if you wear them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":5} -->\n<h5>More comfortable</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Traditional braces cause intense discomfort, and everyone cannot tolerate the pain caused to pressure on the teeth. The tightening of the brackets can also cause painful soreness. As a result, it leads to a cycle of discomfort for the patient.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Invisalign doesn\u2019t use brackets and is more comfortable to wear. It decreases the level of discomfort and uses a material that is highly elastic to move teeth constantly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":5} -->\n<h5>Less duration</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Someone who wears braces must wait five years to straighten their teeth. Whereas Invisalign only takes 1-1.5 years to correct dental issues and help straighten the teeth.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":4} -->\n<h4>Final Words</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now you have understood the benefits of Invisalign, it\u2019s high time to talk to a professional. Invisalign offers more convenience than regular braces and can help you feel more confident. However, it would help if you qualified as a candidate for Invisalign to obtain optimal results. Schedule an appointment with your dentist and boost your smile.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href="tel:925-933-5677">Contact</a>\u00a0your Walnut Creek Dentist, Dr. Tiziana Procopio Towle, DDS at\u00a0<a href="https://pwdds.com/">Procopio Towle Dental Office</a>,\u00a0to know more about the benefits of Invisalign over regular braces.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":5} -->\n<h5>Resource:</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href="https://pwdds.com/invisalign-step-by-step-procedure/">Invisalign Step-By-Step Procedure</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>This media/content or any other on this website does not prescribe, recommend, or prevent any treatment or procedure.\u202fTherefore, we\u202fhighly recommend that you get the advice of a qualified dentist or other medical practitioners regarding your specific dental condition</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',
